{
  "stem": "8784.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "He was preparing some of the machinery for loading and shipment.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "But of course, at that time, we had no idea what his plans were.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "But Schindler, at this point in time, in the summer of 1944, while it was not known to me, maybe it was known to some other people, that Schindler, in fact, did not give up on us, was not willing to surrender us altogether to the fate that would meet us if we were-- if he did not try to protect us.",
      "word_count": 62
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And he evidently began to scheme a new plan that he would-- this industry is so important-- and he obviously convinced the authorities again-- that his industry is important enough to move all his equipment and all his skilled labor to a concentration camp that he would create deep in Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And he needed, obviously, lots of permission to do that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "But after sometimes in October of 1944, when we were ordered-- the 300 of-- or let's put it this way-- when Schindler was ordered to deliver the 300 of us back to Krakow-Plaszow one more time, he already had hatched a-- hatched a plan to build a new factory and a new concentration camp deep in Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "How this would play out with-- with us in the-- in Krakow-Plaszow, we had no idea.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "Nobody spoke to us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "Nobody told us that there is any kind of a list.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "Nobody told us where we are going.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "But in October of 1944, we arrived in Krakow-Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And within days or a week or two, we were loaded on cattle cars in Krakow-Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "The haste was going on at that time in Krakow-Plaszow-- many hangings going on, many shootings going on, killings, brutalities.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "It was a camp in haste to close.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
